#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_flood_protection.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Flood Protection automatically detects and handles various types of abuse, "
"including message flooding and duplicate spam. All detection runs on your "
"side — other users are not affected."
msgstr ""
"Sel Koruma otomatik olarak algılamalar ve çeşitli istismar türlerini ele "
"alır, mesaj seling ve tekrar spam. Tüm algılama sizin tarafınızda çalışır - "
"diğer kullanıcılar etkilenmez."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_flood_protection.html.heex:30
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Flood Threshold: 10 messages in 15 seconds Spam Threshold: 3 duplicates in "
"10 seconds Auto-Ignore Duration: 5 minutes"
msgstr ""
"Sel Threshold: 15 saniye içinde 10 mesaj Spam Threshold: 10 saniyede 3 "
"tekrarlar Auto-Ignore Süre: 5 dakika"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_paste_dialog.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
